# Personal test media (real photos/videos used for manual E2E testing — never commit)
/test/

# Raw gathered datasets (read-only source material — never commit, never edit
# directly; curated fixtures get copied from here into /test/<feature>/
# subfolders instead). Includes Datasets/final_dataset/ — a generated test
# fixture corpus (LFW, dedupe fixtures, synthetic video/GIF clips, real
# people's face images) — see Datasets/final_dataset/PROVENANCE.md for
# contents and licensing.
/Datasets/

